Law
---

   `info.umd.edu' U.S. Supreme Court decisions from 1989 to the present
are stored in the `info/Government/US/SupremeCt' directory.  Each term
has a separate directory (for example, `term1992').  Get the `README'
and `Index' files to help decipher the case numbers.  6 p.m. - 6 a.m.

   `ftp.uu.net' Supreme Court decisions are in the court-opinions
directory.  You'll want to get the index file, which tells you which
file numbers go with which file names.  The decisions come in Word
Perfect and Atex format only.  Available 24 hours a day.


@EndNode

