Macintosh
---------

   `sumex-aim.stanford.edu' This is the premier site for Macintosh
software.  After you log in, switch to the info-mac directory, which
will bring up a long series of sub-directories of virtually every free
and shareware Mac program you could ever want.  9 p.m. - 9 a.m.

   `ftp.uu.net' You'll find lots of Macintosh programs in the
`systems/mac/simtel20' directory.  Available 24 hours a day.


