directory holds programs that let MS-DOS users connect directly with
UUCP sites. In the info directory, you'll find information about ftp
and ftp sites.  The inet directory contains information about Internet.
Available 24 hours.

   `rtfm.mit.edu' This site contains all available FAQs "frequently
asked questions" files for Usenet newsgroups in the `pub/usenet'
directory. For easy access, get the `index' file.  See under Books
@{"Books" Link "Books"} for a caveat in using this ftp site.  6 p.m. - 6 a.m.

   `ftp.uni-stuttgart.de' In directory `/pub/doc/faq' resides a mirror
of `rtfm.mit.edu'.  Available 24 hours.


