Agriculture
-----------

   `cyfer.esusda.gov' More agricultural statistics and regulations than
most people will ever need.

   `usda.mannlib.cornell.edu' More than 140 different types of
agricultural data, most in Lotus 1-2-3 spreadsheet format.


@EndNode

