@Next "Gopher Disability"
@Prev "Gopher Census"
@Toc "Some Interesting Gophers"

Computers
---------

   `wuarchive.wustl.edu' Dozens of directories with software for all
sorts of computers.  Most programs have to be "un-compressed" before
you can use them.

   `sumex-aim.stanford.edu' A similar type of system, with the emphasis
on Macintosh programs and files.


@EndNode

