   `helix.nih.gov' The National Cancer Institute provides detailed
factsheets on different cancers.  Select "Health and clinical
information" and then "Cancernet information."

   `nysernet.org' Look for information on breast cancer in the "Special
Collections: Breast Cancer" menu.

   `welchlink.welch.jhu.edu' This is Johns Hopkins University's medical
gopher.


