@Node "Others" "bdgtti-2.2.guide/Others"
@Prev "E-mail"
@Toc "FYI Addresses"

FTP'able & Gopher'able Addresses
--------------------------------

   `ftp.eff.org' In directory `/pub/agitprop' you'll find the contents
of a disk containing "Literacy Freeware" by Bruce Sterling.

   In directory `/pub/cud' you'll find the "Computer underground Digest"
archives.

   `gopher.well.sf.ca.us' Gopher this site and browse through the
index. It's full of e-text publications.

   `tic.com' In directory `Bruce Sterling's agitprop/' you'll find the
contents of the "Literacy Freeware" disk by Bruce Sterling.

                                        *"And all else is literature."*
                                    -- Paul Verlaine, The Sun, New York
                                 While he was city editor in 1873-1890.


@EndNode

